<h2 id="integration-requirements">Integration Requirements & Considerations</h2>

<div class="prose max-w-none">
<p>Modern HVAC estimating software doesn't operate in isolation. Key integrations include:</p>

<p><strong>Accounting Systems:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>QuickBooks Online/Desktop (all platforms support)</li>
<li>Sage 50/100 (ServiceTitan, WintacPRO)</li>
<li>Xero (Jobber, Housecall Pro)</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Distributor Connections:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Ferguson, Johnstone Supply, Watsco (major platforms)</li>
<li>Local distributors (varies by software)</li>
<li>Real-time pricing updates: $25-$50/month additional</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Payment Processing:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Credit card processing: 2.6-3.5% + $0.30 per transaction</li>
<li>ACH payments: 0.8-1.5% per transaction</li>
<li>Financing partners: Wells Fargo, Synchrony, Hearth</li>
</ul>

